Brownfield land

View data from publication

Data extracted from a brownfield land data resource collected by the digital land platform.

Collected from:
http://files.datapress.com/london/dataset/brownfield-land-register/2017-12-21T14:21:59.58/London_Brownfield_Land_Register_20171221_.csv
Published 22 May 2018
From:
London Borough of Hammersmith & Fulham

Processing the resource

After being collected the resource is processed. The processing attempts to clean up the brownfield data contained in the resource. It removes things that do not look like data and corrects any data points it can recognise and that look like they need converted in to the required format.

You can read more about how the digital land platform processes the data.

Related content

  • Validation result
  • Preprocessed resource file

About the data

There are a total of 1079 brownfield sites including 0 with an end-date.

These sites total 1399.48 hectares of land.

This has the potential to provide between a minimum of 0 and a maximum of 0 dwellings.

There are 0 sites that have permission in principle.
